# {Client Name} — Campaign Registry

Per `core/methodology/CAMPAIGN_REGISTRY_STANDARD.md`. Maps human campaign references (*"Glamour"*, *"Húsvét"*, *"Black Friday"*) to precise date windows for `/nexus-answer` and related skills.

The registry resolves *which window?* before any campaign analysis begins. Without it, the skill cannot answer *"hogyan teljesített az akciónk"* — it falls into Phase B disambiguation.

