Field reference (full schema in CAMPAIGN_REGISTRY_STANDARD.md §What the registry contains):
- `id` — stable slug (e.g., `glamour-2026-spring`); never changes
- `name_short` — what the team CALLS it in conversation
- `start` / `end` — ISO dates, first/last live day
- `status` — `scheduled` / `active` / `ended` / `cancelled`
- `entities` — list of entity_ids that participated

