## When to update

| Trigger | Action |
|---|---|
| New campaign approved | Add row, `status: scheduled` |
| Campaign goes live | Update to `status: active`, confirm `start` |
| Campaign ends | Update to `status: ended`, confirm `end`, add notes |
| New short name surfaces | Add to `aliases` |
| Disambiguation answer from `/nexus-answer` | Auto-registered by Phase C |
